# Example cron job for automated gleaning extraction
#
# This extracts gleanings daily at 11 PM
#
# To install:
#   1. Edit this file with your actual paths
#   2. Run: crontab -e
#   3. Add the line below
#
# Format: minute hour day month weekday command
#
# Daily at 11 PM:
0 23 * * * /path/to/temoa/scripts/extract_and_reindex.sh >> /path/to/temoa/logs/cron.log 2>&1

# Or every 6 hours:
# 0 */6 * * * /path/to/temoa/scripts/extract_and_reindex.sh >> /path/to/temoa/logs/cron.log 2>&1

# Or weekly on Sunday at 10 PM:
# 0 22 * * 0 /path/to/temoa/scripts/extract_and_reindex.sh >> /path/to/temoa/logs/cron.log 2>&1
